{"tid":2109872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［RTHK好波］警方：721曾派便裝警員在場視察","createTime":"2020-07-15T13:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T03:47:55.000Z","uid":2832,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7a62d1054668709e23fa22f4c3a2ea33706e650b","tid":2109872,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"【警方：721曾派便裝警員在場視察　承諾徹查到底】<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，留意到有傳媒報道跟進去年721元朗事件，提及當日有懷疑便裝警務人員行經元朗鳳攸北街，卻沒有對集結人羣採取行動。警方表示，當日元朗警區曾派出便裝警員到人羣集結的地方視察，因應現場情況及風險評估，作出部署及行動。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，明白公眾對事件的關注，一直鍥而不捨調查，從未間斷，至今拘捕37人，當中7人已被控以參與暴動及串謀有意圖而傷人等。另外，部分涉案疑犯正被警方通緝，不排除有更多人被捕。由於部分案件已交由法庭審理，警方的調查及部署仍在積極進行，不適宜在現階段透露案件細節，但承諾會徹查到底。"},{"pid":"657286146d39c017e0f2d9b8d01a140c27f62d5b","tid":2109872,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/or4B7NpHwbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2For4B7NpHwbY&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=ca01657a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/or4B7NpHwbY</a>"},{"pid":"c2b2963c8249446b701fef194f19d763dfd39390","tid":2109872,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗真係狗"},{"pid":"e9cc84154469516dfc3c945de63eaf1211f4db1c","tid":2109872,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"847a64e7abffdf35ce996b81278f6d6a3796893f","tid":2109872,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"借個位唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初選成功就打飛機?數據話你知9月個勢危到仆街!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2109878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2109878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3be5a556d8b7d08534c7bafb8ab2768c84e9a49","tid":2109872,"uid":335434,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"